item.title: Help with client hacking
item.dc:creator: @Dell Dell
item.description:
@Dell wrote:

Endar is not an open client, if it doesnt have notepads like a source, then its not a open client, in the client hacking area there is a tut and downloadables on clients and stuff…

The Cache:
The cache is kinda like a file that supports everything, its what gives the client its graphics its music, and its items…

If you need a open client, already edited, with textures and stuff like that pm me on everything you want, and ill gladly make one for you…
